Package com.jgaap.languages

Class Summary
Arabic Representation of arabic in jgaap using ISO-8859-6
Chinese A generic chinese representation using GB2123 that does not parse the documents.
ChineseBMM A Chinese representation that uses GB2123 and backwards word matching.
ChineseFMM A Chinese representation that uses GB2123 and forwards word matching.
ChineseJointMM Representation of Chinese in jgaap using GB2123 and a joint matching technique for parsing it into words.
